text:
Attended Jurong Tamil Methodist Church.
Service at level 3..
Moving Worship and awesome word.
Church starts at 4PM.

Very nice and big building. There is a Jurong Christian Kindergarten there along with 3 other churches sharing the same building (on different levels). Huge car park on level 1 and B1 that is free. Disable friendly parking and lifts.

There is a bicycle clinic for free for the public, every Sunday 3-4pm. You will meet very friendly people like Patrick, Daniel and even Freddie who will provide basic maintenance for the bikes. They are volunteers and make themselves available for whoever is in need of a bicycle fix!
I also dropped in for a chat at times!
A shoutout to them, "Thanks for giving my bicycle a new life!"

Funny church funny staff. One of the staff called Chris pray also pray wrong .anyhow take other people water bottle to refill as the water make people sick stress anxiety worry depression sucdiual panic fear. THINK OF OTHERS NOT JUST FOR YOURSELF. She keep talking so soft as headache . Already say do not talk about other church still want to talk . Headache .

Reborn (Born Again) in this Church! God's Presence And His Blessings Is Very Real And Tangible! Words could not Describe the Vibrancy Of This Church, Come And Taste Him! For He Is Like Honey In The Rock!
